ISLAMABAD, Aug 29 (APP): Minister for Information and Broadcasting Marriyum Aurangzeb said on Monday that Pakistan Muslim League-Nawaz leader Maryam Nawaz Sharif, will visit Taunsa Sharif today to express solidarity with the flood victims.
Using her twitter, the minister said during her visit Maryam Nawaz will meet the people in the flood-affected areas.
